Because of instant ramyeon,

460
00:22:55,808 --> 00:22:59,211
you need to stop by
a Hangang River convenience store

461
00:22:59,278 --> 00:23:00,512
this time of the year.

462
00:23:02,648 --> 00:23:05,217
It's really delicious and kind of fun.

